And I tell

972
00:51:16,282 --> 00:51:20,995
{\an8}Memo Vazquez, "Ask Tuca
what he thinks about Galindo?"

973
00:51:21,621 --> 00:51:24,123
{\an8}While he found out,
I talk to Hugo.

