00:52:07,333 --> 00:52:08,668
For him, it was,

991
00:52:09,335 --> 00:52:12,880
and I daresay, unbearable
to be on the bench.

992
00:52:13,506 --> 00:52:16,717
<i>In a game that went into overtime</i>

993
00:52:18,052 --> 00:52:20,346
