994
00:52:20,972 --> 00:52:24,183
It was strange for us
that there were no changes,

995
00:52:24,559 --> 00:52:26,269
but they were warming up.

996
00:52:26,769 --> 00:52:28,312
Those two were warming up.

997
00:52:28,771 --> 00:52:32,608
