1003
00:52:58,801 --> 00:53:01,095
<i>He gets up confidently
and goes to Hugo.</i>

1004
00:53:01,178 --> 00:53:04,348
<i>He wanted me as midfielder
to replace Benjamin Galindo.</i>

1005
00:53:04,515 --> 00:53:07,059
I have never played there.

1006
00:53:07,518 --> 00:53:08,769
And right now in the game

1007
00:53:08,853 --> 00:53:11,898
I said, "I can go get them."

1008
00:53:12,148 --> 00:53:15,026
<i>If everyone does everything right,</i>

1009
00:53:15,651 --> 00:53:17,445
<i>why do I have to change that?</i>

