that you don't know if will work.

1015
00:53:32,668 --> 00:53:35,421
And that's why you have to refresh.

1016
00:53:37,131 --> 00:53:40,801
It's the stupidest thing
I've ever heard.

1017
00:53:42,386 --> 00:53:43,888
Wait a minute!

1018
00:53:45,014 --> 00:53:47,183
If they are doing thing well,

1019
00:53:47,600 --> 00:53:49,727
why do I have to change someone?

1020
00:53:50,937 --> 00:53:54,523
<i>When he warms up,
I go by the stripe and ask, "What?"</i>

1021
00:54:10,706 --> 00:54:13,125
<i>That dialogue on the bench</i>

