I loved him dearly.

1113
00:58:19,288 --> 00:58:20,372
<i>Are you not friends anymore?</i>

1114
00:58:20,456 --> 00:58:21,999
We're not friends.

1115
00:58:28,797 --> 00:58:29,882
Yeah.

1116
00:58:30,507 --> 00:58:32,718
It happens to everyone,
specially at my age.

1117
00:58:32,801 --> 00:58:34,094
I'm sure it does.

