00:59:22,726 --> 00:59:24,103
<i>my last three goals.</i>

1134
00:59:25,229 --> 00:59:28,816
<i>He didn't train once in Real Madrid,</i>

1135
00:59:29,108 --> 00:59:30,859
<i>not because he didn't want to train.</i>

1136
00:59:31,068 --> 00:59:32,861
<i>Real Madrid was not doing well
in the League.</i>

1137
00:59:33,070 --> 00:59:35,447
<i>Hugo said,
"The tribute is approaching.</i>

1138
00:59:35,614 --> 00:59:38,492
<i>To train under pressure
with the team</i>

1139
00:59:38,742 --> 00:59:40,577
<i>will only make me
distract them."</i>

1140
00:59:41,412 --> 00:59:42,329
<i>It's incredible</i>

1141
00:59:42,413 --> 00:59:43,998
<i>that he went to Majadahonda,</i>

