01:01:21,178 --> 01:01:25,224
or his fears with others,

1175
01:01:25,307 --> 01:01:30,562
I mean, with his closest
family members, because

1176
01:01:31,021 --> 01:01:33,607
he prefers, somehow,

1177
01:01:33,690 --> 01:01:36,985
