and his pain to others,

1178
01:01:37,069 --> 01:01:42,741
like when he shares
that suffering with us.

1179
01:01:43,409 --> 01:01:45,035
I mean,

1180
01:01:46,203 --> 01:01:49,039
the time I saw him
suffer the most

